		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />First scroll tests.<br />The engine used for this scroll is the All-direction scrolling (with small modifications), by Doug Fraker.<br />Its peculiarity lies in that it works under the NES 4-screen format.<br />I have to solve errors.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FFKp4oZ21F8">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FFKp4oZ21F8</a><!-- m -->

		

