		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's what the original game is like. Or well, almost. They are really &quot;low hanging&quot; clouds.<br /><br />Honestly, I think it's an artistic freedom games should be able to take. I love scrolling clouds like that. Nothing to build a creepy atmosphere like <a href="https://youtu.be/xK2GvbzMM9Y?t=2m41s" class="postlink">SOTN-style fast clouds</a>, too.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
